<div class="home-container">
  <h1 class="title-h1">How it works</h1>

  <div style="text-align: center;">
    <%= image_tag('dark_map.png', class: "home-carousel-image") %>
  </div>
  <h2>1. Create an event</h2>

  <div class="how-it-works">
    <ul>
      <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Give it a name and date but no location.</li>
      <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Just tell us who you are, where you're travelling from and if you'd prefer to meet in a cafe, bar or restaurant.</li>
      <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Choose the period your friends have to join (like four hours, or one day).</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div style="text-align: center;">
   <%= image_tag('biking.png', class: "home-carousel-image") %>
  </div>
  <h2>2. Share with friends</h2>

  <div class="how-it-works">
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <ul>
      <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> We create a unique event link which you can share with friends.</li>
      <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> They join and say where they are travelling from (by entering an address or sharing their geolocation).</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div style="text-align: center;">
    <%= image_tag('having_fun.png', class: "home-carousel-image") %>
  </div>
  <h2>3. We tell you where to meet</h2>
  <div class="how-it-works">
    <p><p>
    <p></p>
    <ul>
      <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Once the joining period is up, we calculate the central point of all attendees (excluding anyone who is just too far away).</li>
      <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> We then recommend a nearby bar, cafe or restaurant that works for everyone and notify the group.</li>
      <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> If the event creator is not happy with the venue, they can try their luck and 'Spin again'.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

</div>
